'''2016年全英音乐奖'''（{{lang-en|2016 Brit Awards}}）于2016年2月24举行，是第36届[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]年度流行音乐大奖。颁奖典礼在伦敦O2体育场举办，[[Ant_&_Dec|Ant & Dec]]第三次担纲主持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brits.co.uk/news/ant-dec-return-to-host-the-brits-2016|title=Ant & Dec return for The BRITs 2016|publisher=The BRIT Awards|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2016-02-28|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806223700/http://www.brits.co.uk/news/ant-dec-return-to-host-the-brits-2016|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。提名名单2016年1月14日公布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/brits/news/2016-date-venue-hosts/|title=BRIT Awards 2016: Justin Bieber AND Coldplay Join Adele As Confirmed Performers|publisher=Capital FM|date=2015-12-18|accessdate=2016-02-28|archive-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326153507/http://www.capitalfm.com/brits/news/2016-date-venue-hosts/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，英国服装设计师{{le|帕姆·霍格|Pam Hogg}}为今年的颁奖典礼设计了以全英音乐奖雕塑为造型的奖杯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brits.co.uk/news/pam-hogg-revealed-as-brits-statue-designer|title=Pam Hogg revealed as BRITs Trophy Designer|publisher=BRIT Awards|date=2015-11-29|accessdate=2016-02-28|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201523/http://www.brits.co.uk/news/pam-hogg-revealed-as-brits-statue-designer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。仪式特设致敬环节，由[[安妮·蓝妮克丝|安妮·蓝妮克丝]]主持纪念已故英国乐坛巨星[[大卫·鲍伊|大卫·鲍伊]]，[[加里·奥德曼|加里·奥德曼]]发布纪念演讲，[[洛德_(歌手)|洛德]]与鲍伊的长期伴奏组合进行表演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-35289998|title=David Bowie: Brit Awards tribute for 'visionary' musician|date=2016-01-12|publisher=BBC|access-date=2016-01-12|archive-date=2017-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128122205/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-35289998|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/live/2016/feb/24/brit-awards-2016-with-adele-coldplay-justin-bieber-and-more-live|title=Brit awards 2016 with Adele, Coldplay, Justin Bieber and more – as it happened|date=2016-02-24|work=Guardian|accessdate=2016-02-25|archive-date=2016-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160224175834/http://www.theguardian.com/music/live/2016/feb/24/brit-awards-2016-with-adele-coldplay-justin-bieber-and-more-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

